{"ID":"20250919163918-a6s1l5x","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250919163918-a6s1l5x","title":"05 预训练、提示和预测：自然语言处理中提示方法的系统性调查","type":"doc","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-dp2tq5e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-dp2tq5e","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"摘要 (Abstract)"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-qwer6i9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-qwer6i9","updated":"20250921102542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本文对自然语言处理领域中一个我们称之为“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”（prompt-based learning）的新范式下的研究工作进行了综述和梳理。与传统的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"监督学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（supervised learning）——即训练一个模型接收输入 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 并预测输出 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 为 P(y|x)——不同，提示学习是基于直接对文本概率进行建模的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。为了使用这些模型来执行预测任务，原始输入 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 会通过一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模板"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（template）被修改为一个带有未填充槽位的文本字符串"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示 x'"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，然后语言模型被用来概率性地填充这些未填充的信息，以获得一个最终的字符串 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x̂"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并从"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x̂"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中推导出最终的输出 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这个框架之所以强大且富有吸引力，原因有以下几点：它允许语言模型在海量的原始文本上进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（pre-trained），并且通过定义一个新的提示函数，模型能够执行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"少样本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（few-shot）甚至"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"零样本学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（zero-shot learning），从而在只有很少或没有标记数据的情况下适应新的场景。在本文中，我们介绍了这一前景广阔的范式的基本概念，描述了一套能够覆盖各种现有工作的统一数学符号体系，并从多个维度对现有工作进行了梳理，例如，预训练语言模型的选择、提示以及微调策略。为了让感兴趣的初学者更容易入门，我们不仅对现有工作进行了系统性的回顾，并构建了一个高度结构化的提示学习概念类型学，还发布了其他资源，例如一个名为 NLPedia-Pretrain 的网站，其中包含了持续更新的综述和论文列表。"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-i1c0579","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-i1c0579","updated":"20250921102542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919164605-5r4llum","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-5r4llum","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-z6rx9wr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-z6rx9wr","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这段摘要精炼地介绍了一种名为“提示学习”（Prompt-based Learning）的自然语言处理新范式，并阐明了其核心思想、优势以及本文的主要贡献。"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-ga0b14a","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-ga0b14a","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心概念：范式转变"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-qi7rvog","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-qi7rvog","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-ufm7tb3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-ufm7tb3","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-3kdjtuk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-3kdjtuk","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"对比传统方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：文章首先明确地将"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"传统监督学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进行对比。传统方法是训练一个模型去学习一个特定的映射关系 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"P(y|x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（例如，给定一句话 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，判断其情感 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 是积极还是消极）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-qqjtzph","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-qqjtzph","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-kf3109q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-kf3109q","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示学习的思路"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：提示学习则完全不同。它不改变模型，而是改变"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"输入"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它将原始任务（如情感分类）重新构建成一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更熟悉的形式——“完形填空”。例如，将句子“我喜欢这部电影”转化为一个带空槽的提示：“我喜欢这部电影。总的来说，这是一部 [__] 的电影。”然后，让预训练好的语言模型去预测空槽里最可能出现的词（如“精彩”），从而得到最终的分类结果。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-217wc0x","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-217wc0x","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"工作流程拆解"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-2qcmpo1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-2qcmpo1","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"摘要清晰地描述了提示学习的四个关键步骤："}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-2ho5tw5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-2ho5tw5","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-iunmcls","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-iunmcls","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-mxtv0ik","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-mxtv0ik","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"输入转换 (Input Transformation)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：原始输入 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 通过一个预设的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模板 (template)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 转换成一个带槽的提示 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x'"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-wpx1cda","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-wpx1cda","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-609gfhn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-609gfhn","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"槽位填充 (Slot Filling)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：强大的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"利用其学到的海量知识，概率性地预测并填充 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x'"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 中的槽位，生成完整的字符串 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x̂"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-30stpnb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-30stpnb","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-7btte4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-7btte4b","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"答案映射 (Answer Mapping)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：从填充好的字符串 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"x̂"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 中提取出关键信息（例如，填充的词是“精彩”）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-rbczgzz","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-rbczgzz","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-vjyqtoq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-vjyqtoq","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"推导输出 (Deriving Output)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：将提取的信息映射回原始任务的最终输出 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（例如，“精彩”→“积极”）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-8w48xou","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-8w48xou","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心优势：为何强大？"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-yx3jdjz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-yx3jdjz","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-6pc4hwh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-6pc4hwh","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-z3iwf7c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-z3iwf7c","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"释放预训练潜力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：它允许模型在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"海量的无标签原始文本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上进行预训练，充分利用了互联网上的巨量数据。这使得模型能够学习到非常广泛和深入的语言知识。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-fq7okaq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-fq7okaq","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-6uma515","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-6uma515","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实现小样本/零样本学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：最大的吸引力在于，通过精心设计提示，模型可以在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"几乎没有（零样本）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 或"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"只有极少数（少样本）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 标注样本的情况下，快速适应新任务。这极大地降低了对昂贵的人工标注数据的依赖，使得模型部署和适应新场景变得更加高效和灵活。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-h39il6n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-h39il6n","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"本文的贡献"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-w4n120w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-w4n120w","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这篇论文本身是一篇"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综述性文章"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，其目标是为这个新兴领域建立一个系统的框架。具体贡献包括："}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-xyf6vn8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-xyf6vn8","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-fowun9s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-fowun9s","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-rzsbl0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-rzsbl0k","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"介绍基础"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：为初学者普及提示学习的基本概念。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-47bircx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-47bircx","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-dzl9rfb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-dzl9rfb","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"统一符号"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：建立一套通用的数学语言，以整合和描述该领域内多样化的工作。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-heuu0pu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-heuu0pu","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-iccac4n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-iccac4n","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"系统梳理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：从模型、提示、微调策略等多个维度对现有研究进行分类和组织。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-3fqi6s6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-3fqi6s6","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919164605-o6gmu2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-o6gmu2j","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"资源共享"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：发布了如 NLPedia-Pretrain 网站等配套资源，方便研究者跟踪最新进展。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-sufyrsa","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-sufyrsa","updated":"20250921102542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919164605-5vyao9n","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-5vyao9n","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综合性解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-i4ky2a9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-i4ky2a9","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这段摘要宣告了自然语言处理领域的一次重要"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"范式革命"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：从“为每个任务训练一个新模型”的传统思路，转向“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用一个统一的大模型，通过不同的提示来解决所有任务"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”。"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-ywike51","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-ywike51","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其核心思想是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最大化地利用预训练语言模型（PLMs）内部已经存储的庞大世界知识和语言能力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。传统微调（Fine-tuning）方式虽然有效，但它实际上是在强行改变模型的结构和参数以适应特定任务，这不仅需要大量的标注数据，也可能损害模型原有的通用性。"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-2w1hlks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-2w1hlks","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相比之下，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示学习则是一种更“非侵入式”的、更符合语言模型“天性”的方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。它不去修改模型，而是通过巧妙地设计“问题”（即提示），引导模型从其浩瀚的知识库中“回忆”或“推理”出答案。这种方法之所以能够实现惊人的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"少样本甚至零样本学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能力，正是因为它将下游任务与模型的预训练目标（通常是文本生成或完形填空）在形式上统一了起来，使得模型能够直接应用其在预训练阶段学到的能力，而无需大量的任务特定训练。"}]},{"ID":"20250919164605-tnsb612","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919164605-tnsb612","updated":"20250919164605"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结而言，这段文字不仅定义了“提示学习”，更阐明了其背后的哲学——即"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"从“改造模型以适应任务”转向“重构任务以适应模型”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这一转变极大地提升了NLP模型的通用性、灵活性和数据效率，为后续以GPT-3为代表的超大规模模型的“上下文学习”（in-context learning）能力奠定了理论基础。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-q3y96qe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-q3y96qe","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1 自然语言处理领域的两大浪潮 (TWO SEA CHANGES IN NATURAL LANGUAGE PROCESSING)"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-705buhz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-705buhz","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完全监督学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Fully supervised learning），即针对目标任务，仅在一个由输入-输出样本组成的数据集上训练一个任务专属模型的方法，长期以来在许多机器学习任务中扮演着核心角色，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自然语言处理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（NLP）也不例外。由于这类手动标注的数据集不足以训练出高质量的模型，早期的NLP模型严重依赖于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特征工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（feature engineering）（表1(a)；例如，Guyon等人，Lafferty等人，Och等人，Zhang和Nivre），在这一阶段，NLP研究人员利用他们的领域知识来定义和从原始数据中提取显著特征，并为模型提供有用的归纳偏置（inductive bias）以便从有限的数据中学习。随着神经网络模型的出现，NLP的显著特征可以与模型训练联合学习，因此焦点转移到了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"架构工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（architecture engineering），即归纳偏置更多地通过精心设计的、有助于学习此类特征的神经网络架构来提供（表1(b)；例如，Bahdanau等人，Chung等人，Hochreiter和Schmidhuber，Kalchbrenner等人，Kim，Vaswani等人）。¹"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-07ga52d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-07ga52d","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然而，从2017年到2019年，NLP和这种完全监督学习的模式经历了一场巨变，其扮演的角色日益缩小。具体来说，标准范式转变为“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练和微调"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”（pre-train and fine-tune）范式（表1(c)；例如，Dong等人，Lewis等人，Peters等人，Radford等人，Yang等人）。在这种范式中，一个带有固定架构的模型首先被"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言模型（LM）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ³，来预测所观察到的文本数据的概率。因为训练语言模型所需的原始文本数据非常丰富，这些语言模型可以在大规模数据集上进行训练，并在此过程中学习到稳健的、通用的语言特征。之后，这个预训练好的语言模型会通过引入额外的参数，并使用任务特定的目标函数进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"微调"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，来适应不同的下游任务。在这种范式下，焦点转向了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"目标工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（objective engineering），即设计在预训练和微调阶段都使用的训练目标。例如，Zhang等人的研究表明，引入一个预测文档中显著句子的损失函数，有助于提升预训练语言模型在文本摘要任务上的微调效果。基本上，预训练语言模型的主体部分被保留下来，并（不总是；Peters等人）进行微调，使其更适合解决下游任务。"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-npxfrwz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-npxfrwz","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在，在撰写本文之时，我们正处于第二场巨变的浪潮中，在这种浪潮下，“预训练、微调”的流程被一个我们称之为“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练、提示和预测"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”（pre-train, prompt, and predict）的新流程所取代。在这个范式中，下游任务被重新表述，使其看起来更像原始语言模型在训练时解决过的那些任务。这些任务是在一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"文本提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（textual prompt）的帮助下解决的。例如，在识别一条社交媒体帖子的情感时，对于“我错过了今天的公交车”这句话，我们可以继续写成“我感觉___”，然后让语言模型用一个带有情感色彩的词来填空。或者，如果我们选择提示“英语：我错过了今天的公交车。法语：___”，那么语言模型就可能会用相应的法语句子来填空。通过选择合适的提示，我们可以"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"操控模型的行为"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，使其能够"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预测"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"出我们想要的输出，有时甚至"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无需任何额外的任务特定训练"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（表1(d)；例如，Brown等人，Petroni等人，Radford等人，Schick和Schütze）。这种方法的优势在于，给定一个合适的提示，一个单一的语言模型，在完全无监督的情况下，可以被用来解决大量不同的任务。然而，由于有前景的提示数量极其庞大，这种方法也引入了对"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prompt engineering）的需求，即寻找最合适的提示，以引导语言模型解决手头的任务。"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-i9wfq1u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-i9wfq1u","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本综述旨在通过对提示方法提供一个概述和形式化定义（第2节），来梳理这个快速发展领域的知识现状。随后是对基础知识的深入探讨，从"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示模板工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prompt template engineering）（第3节）和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示答案工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prompt answer engineering）（第4节），到更高级的概念，如"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多提示学习方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（multi-prompt learning methods）（第5节）和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示感知训练方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prompt-aware training methods）（第6节）。然后，我们组织并讨论了各种已应用的提示学习方法，以及它们如何与提示方法的选择相互作用（第7节）。最后，我们试图将提示方法的现状置于整个研究生态系统中，将其与其他研究领域联系起来（第8节），并提出一些当前可能已成熟、可供进一步研究的挑战性问题（第9节）。"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-obfd7fe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-obfd7fe","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后，为了帮助对该领域感兴趣的初学者更有效地学习，我们重点介绍了一些关于提示学习（以及预训练）的系统性资源，这些资源在本综述和配套网站中都有提供："}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-pyzehqm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-pyzehqm","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-wf3y3y7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-wf3y3y7","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-06v8rot","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-06v8rot","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一个关于提示学习的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"网站"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，其中包含对本综述的频繁更新、相关的幻灯片等。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-36zj4dl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-36zj4dl","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-euduw31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-euduw31","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"图1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：提示学习中重要概念的类型学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-sg76z59","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-sg76z59","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-3431mft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-3431mft","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"表7和表8"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对不同提示方法的系统性和全面性比较。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-wcg88vy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-wcg88vy","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-kidb2i2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-kidb2i2","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"表5"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对常用提示的组织整理。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-0uhaqlt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-0uhaqlt","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-2tywwwb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-2tywwwb","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"表4"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：提示学习研究工作的时间线。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-n0bkfo3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-n0bkfo3","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-4vemjh4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-4vemjh4","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"表1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对不同预训练语言模型的系统性和全面性比较。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-ku3q064","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-ku3q064","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919165049-8mtoqpx","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-8mtoqpx","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-idarug8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-idarug8","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这部分内容宏观地回顾了自然语言处理（NLP）领域的发展历程，并清晰地勾勒出两次深刻的“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"范式革命"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”（原文为“Sea Changes”，意为巨变或浪潮）。"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-qfnlcbv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-qfnlcbv","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"浪潮之前的时代：监督学习"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-hxoy3uj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-hxoy3uj","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作者首先描述了NLP的“古典时期”，这个时期由两种主要方法主导："}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-0dzm37f","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-0dzm37f","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-5gmfmfl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-5gmfmfl","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-mcvg4pi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-mcvg4pi","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特征工程 (Feature Engineering)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 这是最早期的阶段。模型的性能高度依赖于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"人类专家"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"手工设计的特征。研究者的核心工作是利用自己的语言学知识，为模型““喂””最有用的信息。这需要大量的领域知识，且费时费力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-u6lkv2p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-u6lkv2p","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-n7z6ba5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-n7z6ba5","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"架构工程 (Architecture Engineering)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 随着深度学习的兴起，模型（如RNNs, LSTMs）开始能够自动学习特征。于是，研究的重心从“设计特征”转向了“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"设计模型架构"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”。研究者们致力于创造更复杂、更精妙的网络结构，以期获得更好的性能。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-ufwvq2e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-ufwvq2e","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"共同点"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这两个阶段都属于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完全监督学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，即每个任务都需要一个专门的模型和大量的标注数据，成本高昂且通用性差。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-rbol6hh","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-rbol6hh","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919165049-1yxylxt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-1yxylxt","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第一次浪潮：预训练与微调 (Pre-train and Fine-tune)"}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-oplfcpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-oplfcpr","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这是NLP领域的第一次重大革命，其核心思想是“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"两阶段学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”："}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-oes0buw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-oes0buw","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-vhhzxc5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-vhhzxc5","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-8j05k4m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-8j05k4m","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预训练 (Pre-training)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":": 在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"海量的、无标签的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文本数据上训练一个巨大的语言模型。这个阶段的目标是让模型学习通用的语言知识、语法结构和世界常识。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165049-xkj6fbn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-xkj6fbn","updated":"20250919165049"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165049-gdz1n4b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165049-gdz1n4b","updated":"