TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基于提示的训练策略"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：还有一些方法可以训练参数，无论是提示的参数、LM的参数，还是两者的参数。在第6节中，我们总结了不同的策略并详细说明了它们的相对优势。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-qerzcvl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-qerzcvl","updated":"20250919165751"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919165750-arns9h2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-arns9h2","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-r5ugxg7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-r5ugxg7","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这部分内容为整个提示学习框架搭建了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“骨架”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。在用数学语言精确定义了提示的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"三步走（添加提示→搜索答案→映射输出）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"之后，作者指出了实现这一框架的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"五个核心“设计决策点”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-hb71mg7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-hb71mg7","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-xe4htps","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-xe4htps","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-ou66dax","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-ou66dax","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"选对“大脑” (LM Choice)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：基础是什么？用GPT-3（生成式）还是用BERT（填空式）？不同的模型有不同的特长，这是所有工作的第一步。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-99fvyb5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-99fvyb5","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-h5ormca","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-h5ormca","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"设计“问题” (Template Engineering)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：怎么问？是直接问“这部电影怎么样？[Z]”，还是用更含蓄的“总的来说，这是一部[Z]的电影”？问题的问法至关重要。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-ysv6e0x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-ysv6e0x","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-k3ovz34","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-k3ovz34","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"设计“选项” (Answer Engineering)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：答案是什么形式？是让模型从{“好”, “坏”}里选，还是让它自由发挥？选项的设计直接影响任务的难度和最终结果的解析。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-epwpfaw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-epwpfaw","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-f0yxecp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-f0yxecp","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"升级“玩法” (Expanding the Paradigm)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：基本的三步走是不是太简单了？能不能一次用多个提示、或者把复杂问题拆成几个小提示来问？这里探讨的是更高级的组合策略。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-xl6rsxv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-xl6rsxv","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-gm8ixuz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-gm8ixuz","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"