kTextContent":"从模糊到精确"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：在这一章之前，“提示”可能只是一个模糊的“向模型提问”的概念。本章通过定义"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示函数、模板、答案空间、搜索和映射"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"等一系列术语和数学公式，为其赋予了严谨的科学内涵。这使得不同的研究工作可以在一个统一的框架下被比较和理解。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-gvc6lat","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-gvc6lat","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-mn54h69","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-mn54h69","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"统一所有NLP任务"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：本章最具洞察力的一点，是揭示了提示学习如何能够"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"将看似风马牛不相及的NLP任务（分类、生成、标注等）统一到“预测文本概率”这一单一框架下"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。如表3所示，所有任务都被巧妙地“翻译”成了语言模型在预训练时就已熟练掌握的“完形填空”游戏。这种“任务→LM”的根本性转变，是提示学习能够实现高效率和少样本学习的关键所在。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-jhb9fni","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-jhb9fni","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919165750-bxfka26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-bxfka26","updated":"20250919165750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提供了一份“操作手册”和“研究地图”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：通过图1的类型学和2.3节的设计考量，本章为从业者和研究者提供了一份清晰的蓝图。对于一个实际问题，开发者可以按图索骥，从LM选择、模板设计、答案设计、组合策略和训练策略这五个维度去系统地设计和优化解决方案。对于研究者，图中的每一个分支都开辟了一个可以深入探索的研究方向。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919165750-mozbsac","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"heading-fold":"1","id":"20250919165750-mozbsac","updated":"20250921100627"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结而言，第二章是整篇综述的基石。它不仅"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“是什么”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（What）——定义了提示学习，更阐明了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“为什么”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（Why）——它为何能有效，以及"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“怎么办”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（How）——如何系统地设计和研究提示方法。它将提示学习从一门“艺术”变成了一门“科学”，为后续所有技术细节的讨论奠定了坚实的理论基础。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ohcz3su","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ohcz3su","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3 提示模板工程 (PROMPT TEMPLATE ENGINEERING)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-zuxsjjm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-zuxsjjm","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示模板工程"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是创建一个提示函数 f"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"prompt"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(x) 的过程，该函数能在下游任务上获得最佳的模型性能。在许多先前的工作中，这个模型要么是经过精心设计的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"人类工程师"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，要么是为每个任务搜索最佳模板的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"算法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。正如“提示模板工程”部分（图1）所示，我们必须首先考虑"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示的形状"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prompt shape），然后决定是采用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"手动"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"还是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自动化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的方法来创建所需形状的提示，具体如下所述。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-i3a6wp5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-i3a6wp5","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.1 提示形状 (Prompt Shape)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-iiail6v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-iiail6v","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如上所述，提示主要有两种变体："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完形填空提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（cloze prompts），它填充文本字符串的空白（例如，“我喜欢这部电影，它是一部 [Z] 的电影”），和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"前缀提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（prefix prompts），它续写一个字符串（例如，“我喜欢这部电影。这篇评论的感情基调是什么？[Z]”）。两者的选择将取决于手头的任务和用于解决该任务的语言模型。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-jxzqqfk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-jxzqqfk","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总的来说，对于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"文本生成"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"任务，或者使用标准的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自回归语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解决的任务，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"前缀提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"往往更具引导性，因为它们与模型的标准从左到右的特性非常契合。对于使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"掩码语言模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（masked LMs）的任务，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完形填空提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是一个很好的选择，因为它们非常匹配预训练的形式。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"全文重构模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更加通用，可以使用完形填空或前缀提示。最后，对于需要多个输入的任务，例如"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"文本对分类"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，提示模板必须包含两个输入的空间，[X1] 和 [X2]。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-3ssvs2i","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-3ssvs2i","updated":"20250919170807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919170744-lkndg8d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-lkndg8d","updated":"20250919170807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-fsrzazj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-fsrzazj","updated":"20250919170807"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"形状决定适配性"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-yofshxs","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-yofshxs","updated":"20250919170807"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-wraxiv1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-wraxiv1","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-91mwftt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-91mwftt","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：提示的“形状”应该与语言模型的“天性”（即其预训练方式）相匹配，这样才能最大化地发挥模型的能力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-7125m89","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-7125m89","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-wqd0t2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-wqd0t2g","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完形填空 (Cloze) vs. 前缀 (Prefix)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ai3ce8z","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ai3ce8z","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-69clw4s","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-69clw4s","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-fyjyiyw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-fyjyiyw","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完形填空"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ("},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"...[Z]..."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​): 这种形式就像给BERT这类"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"掩码语言模型（Masked LM）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 做它们最熟悉的“完形填空”题。BERT在预训练时就是通过上下文来预测被遮盖的词，因此这种提示形式能最好地激活其学到的双向语境理解能力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-7tmuixm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-7tmuixm","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-jg3r5r2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-jg3r5r2","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"前缀"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ("},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"...[Z]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​): 这种形式则完全符合GPT这类"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自回归语言模型（Autoregressive LM）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的“文本续写”习惯。GPT的任务就是根据前面的文本预测下一个词，因此将答案槽放在最后，就像是让它自然地把话说完。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-92rv7v8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-92rv7v8","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-7cz9us5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-7cz9us5","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"复杂任务的扩展"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于需要处理多个输入的任务（如判断两句话是否矛盾），模板也必须相应地设计多个输入槽 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[X1]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[X2]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，以容纳所有必要信息。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-i6yo02d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-i6yo02d","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-70tt2fl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-70tt2fl","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结论"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：选择哪种形状，首要的考虑因素是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“你用的是哪种类型的语言模型？”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。选对了形状，就等于为模型创造了一个最舒适、最熟悉的工作环境。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-kpndxvw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-kpndxvw","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.2 手动模板工程 (Manual Template Engineering)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-w27hdtk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-w27hdtk","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"创建提示最自然的方式是基于人类的内省来"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"手动创建直观的模板"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。例如，开创性的LAMA数据集手动创建了完形填空模板来探测LM中的知识。Brown等人手动制作了前缀模板来处理各种任务，包括问答、翻译和探测常识推理。Schick和Schütze使用了预定义的模板在少样本设置下进行文本分类和条件文本生成任务。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-9oiv2lh","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-9oiv2lh","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919170744-cdi7gyb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-cdi7gyb","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ondx55t","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ondx55t","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"直觉驱动的艺术"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-1yd2cup","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-1yd2cup","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-pa0g1rp","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-pa0g1rp","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-7d8vmi8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-7d8vmi8","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：依赖人类专家的语言直觉和对任务的理解，手工编写模板。例如，想知道“法国的首都是哪里？”，一个直观的模板就是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"The capital of France is [Z]."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-92q6em5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-92q6em5","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-ug3vsna","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ug3vsna","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"优点"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-d37y0pi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-d37y0pi","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-arqwb9f","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-arqwb9f","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-q65sdsl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-q65sdsl","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"简单直观"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：上手快，易于理解和实现。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-2reggg9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-2reggg9","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-56fcgu0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-56fcgu0","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可解释性强"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：人类可以理解模板为何这样设计。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-tin1r9p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-tin1r9p","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-gxpzwqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-gxpzwqm","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在很多任务上效果不错"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于简单、明确的任务，人类的直觉往往是有效的。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-8nwrydc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-8nwrydc","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-3sz72qv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-3sz72qv","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"缺点"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这是一个“经验活”，高度依赖设计者的水平，缺乏系统性和可复现性。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-766ghwz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-766ghwz","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.3 自动化模板学习 (Automated Template Learning)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-vcm0dis","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-vcm0dis","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然手动创建模板很直观，并且允许解决各种任务并达到一定的准确度，但这种方法也存在几个问题：(1) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"创建和实验提示是一门耗时且需要经验的艺术"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，特别是对于像语义分析这样的复杂任务；(2) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"即使是经验丰富的提示设计者也可能无法手动发现最优的提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-9aev61d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-9aev61d","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了解决这些问题，已经提出了许多方法来自动化模板设计过程。特别地，自动生成的提示可以进一步分为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（discrete prompts），其中提示是实际的文本字符串，和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（continuous prompts），其中提示是直接在底层LM的嵌入空间中描述的。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-jn1n7eb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-jn1n7eb","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另一个正交的设计考量是，提示函数 f"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"prompt"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"(x) 对于每个输入是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"静态的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（static），即对每个输入都使用相同的模板，还是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"动态的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（dynamic），即为每个输入生成一个定制的模板。静态和动态策略都已被用于各种离散和连续的提示，我们将在下文中提到。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-brzjzer","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-brzjzer","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919170744-yyvcjko","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-yyvcjko","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ofj1p34","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ofj1p34","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"从“炼丹”到“自动化”"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ymsswy0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ymsswy0","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-zaltzxa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-zaltzxa","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-5bent35","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-5bent35","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"手动方法的瓶颈"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：作者一针见血地指出了手动设计的两大痛点："}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-b7sxvlc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-b7sxvlc","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-s47z3mr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-s47z3mr","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-udk03p6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-udk03p6","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"高昂的人力成本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：设计、调试、验证提示的过程非常耗时，像一门“手艺活”而非科学。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-fu95qb4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-fu95qb4","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-687pqyl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-687pqyl","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"性能天花板"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：人类的直觉和语言习惯是有限的，我们想出的“好问题”很可能并不是机器眼中“最有效的问题”。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-8vhl808","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-8vhl808","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-87vv6yy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-87vv6yy","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"自动化的两条路径"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：为了突破这些瓶颈，研究转向了自动化方法，并分化出两条截然不同的技术路线："}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-fbcmfuo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-fbcmfuo","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-50szj7q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-50szj7q","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-ix6om7f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ix6om7f","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示 (Discrete Prompts / Hard Prompts)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：目标是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在人类可读的词汇空间里，自动搜索或生成最好的文本提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这就像是让机器自己写出 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"The capital of France is [Z]."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 这样的句子。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-maf5xlo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-maf5xlo","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-hc9nlfi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-hc9nlfi","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示 (Continuous Prompts / Soft Prompts)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这是一种更激进、更抽象的方法。它"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"完全放弃了提示必须是人类可读文本的约束"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，认为对模型最有效的“提示”可能是一些无法用自然语言表达的、只存在于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模型嵌入空间中的特定向量"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这就像是直接对模型的大脑进行“微电流刺激”，而不是跟它说话。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-oxkmltu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-oxkmltu","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-3c9oz6x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-3c9oz6x","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"静态 vs. 动态"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这是一个额外的维度，意味着无论是离散还是连续提示，都可以选择是“一个模板走天下”（静态），还是“为每个输入量身定做一个模板”（动态）。动态方法通常更灵活，但实现也更复杂。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-7dz23l1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-7dz23l1","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.3.1 离散提示 (Discrete Prompts)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-fs4tovz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-fs4tovz","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"致力于发现"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（也称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"硬提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）的研究工作，是在一个离散空间中自动搜索模板，通常对应于自然语言短语。我们详细介绍几种已提出的方法。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-2wevvsm","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-2wevvsm","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-nxdxeup","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-nxdxeup","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-esam8ac","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-esam8ac","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D1：提示挖掘 (Prompt Mining)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。Jiang等人提出的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"MINE"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是一种基于挖掘的方法，可以自动为一组训练输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和输出"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"找到模板。该方法在大型文本语料库（例如，维基百科）中搜索，并找到连接字符串"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的中间词或依赖路径。或者，在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"之间的频繁中间词或依赖路径可以作为 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[X]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 中间词 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[Z]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 形式的模板。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-5tcg3rc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-5tcg3rc","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-ydt4hpw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ydt4hpw","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D2：提示改写 (Prompt Paraphrasing)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。基于改写的方法采用一个现有的种子提示（例如，手动构建或挖掘出的），将其改写成一组候选提示，然后选择在目标任务上训练准确率最高的一个。这种改写可以通过多种方式完成，包括使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"返译"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将提示翻译到另一种语言再翻译回来，用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同义词词典"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中的同义词替换短语，或使用经过专门优化的神经释义重写器来提高准确性。Haviv等人优化了一个神经提示重写器，以便在输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"被插入提示后执行改写，从而允许为每个输入生成不同的提示。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-v5np2u2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-v5np2u2","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-v01dnrt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-v01dnrt","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D3：基于梯度的搜索 (Gradient-based Search)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。Wallace等人应用了一种基于梯度的搜索来寻找能触发预训练LM生成期望目标的简短序列。这是通过一个迭代过程完成的，逐步替换提示中的词元。在此基础上，Shin等人使用梯度下降来自动搜索模板词元，并在性能强大的生成场景中展示了其有效性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-1bx8lcn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-1bx8lcn","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-o2qdkqa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-o2qdkqa","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D4：提示生成 (Prompt Generation)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。其他工作将提示的生成视为一个文本生成任务，并利用标准的自然语言生成模型来执行此任务。例如，Gao等人引入了预训练的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"seq2seq模型T5"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"到模板搜索过程中。由于T5已被预训练用于填空任务，他们使用T5通过(1)将插入模板词元的任务定位为模板，和(2)使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"强化学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来生成模板以控制文本生成来生成模板词元。Ben-David等人提出了一个领域自适应算法，训练T5生成唯一的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"领域相关特征（DRFs）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（一组能够表征领域信息的关键词）。然后，这些DRFs可以与输入拼接形成一个模板，并被下游任务进一步使用。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-rcg2bvn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-rcg2bvn","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-13xppnl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-13xppnl","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D5：提示评分 (Prompt Scoring)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。Davison等人研究了知识库补全任务，并设计了一个模板，使用LM来完成一个（头实体-关系-尾实体）的三元组。他们首先手工制作一组模板作为候选，并填充输入和答案槽以形成一个填充后的提示。然后，他们使用一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"单向LM"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来为这些填充后的提示打分，选择LM概率最高的那个。这将为每个输入得到一个定制的模板。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-d70qxft","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-d70qxft","updated":"20250919171124"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3.3.2 连续提示 (Continuous Prompts)"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-1mrqs9p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-1mrqs9p","updated":"20250919170745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因为提示构建的目的是找到一种能让LM有效执行任务的方法，而不是为了人类消费，所以没有必要将提示限制在人类可解释的自然语言上。因此，存在一些方法"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在模型的嵌入空间中直接执行提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，我们称之为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（也称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"软提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）。具体来说，连续提示消除了两个约束：(1)放宽了模板的嵌入是自然语言（例如，英语）单词的嵌入的限制，以及(2)消除了模板由预训练LM的参数参数化的限制。相反，模板有自己的参数，可以根据下游任务的训练数据进行调整。我们重点介绍几种代表性方法。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-jjclwbf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-jjclwbf","updated":"20250921104208"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-qs0fyv8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-qs0fyv8","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-nus7z62","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-nus7z62","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"C1：前缀微调 (Prefix Tuning)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Prefix Tuning"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 在输入的开头附加一个由连续的任务特定向量组成的序列，同时保持LM参数冻结。在数学上，这包括在给定一个可训练的前缀矩阵 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"M"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong sub","TextMarkTextContent":"φ"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和一组固定的预训练LM参数 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"θ"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的情况下，优化以下对数似然目标函数：\nmax"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"φ"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" log P(y|x; φ; θ) = max"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"φ"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" Σ log P(y"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"|h; θ)\n在公式(2)中，h = [h"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"(1)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"; ...; h"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"(m)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"] 是在时间步i的所有神经网络层的隐状态拼接。它由前缀"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"M"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong sub","TextMarkTextContent":"φ"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中的参数[h"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sub","TextMarkTextContent":"i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"M"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong sub","TextMarkTextContent":"φ[i]"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"]计算得出，否则由预训练LM计算。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实验上，Li和Liang发现，这种连续的、基于前缀的学习在低数据设置下比离散提示更敏感，效果更好。同样，Lester等人提出了用特殊词元来提示，然后微调这些词元的嵌入以适应下游任务。与Li和Liang的方法不同，这种方法引入的额外可调参数更少，因为它不会在每个网络层内添加可调参数。Tsimpoukelli等人训练一个视觉编码器，将图像编码为一系列嵌入，可以用来提示一个冻结的自回归LM生成适当的图像标题。他们展示了这种方法在视觉问答等任务上表现良好。从上面两项工作中可以看出，[参考文献135]中使用的前缀是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"独立于任务嵌入的表示"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ic8wv70","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ic8wv70","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-royorti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-royorti","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"C2：使用离散提示初始化的微调 (Tuning Initialized with Discrete Prompts)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。还有一些方法，它们通过一个已经使用离散提示搜索方法创建或发现的搜索来初始化连续提示。例如，Zhong等人首先使用诸如AUTOPROMPT之类的离arrete搜索方法定义一个模板，然后将模板的词元符号化，并微调这些词元的嵌入以提高任务准确性。这项工作发现，用手动模板初始化可以为搜索过程提供一个更好的起点。Qin和Eisner建议学习一个混合的软提示，其中每个模板的权重和参数都通过训练样本共同学习。他们使用的模板集要么是手动制作的，要么是通过“提示挖掘”方法获得的。同样地，Hambardzumyan等人介绍了一种使用模板的连续范式，并将其初始化为手动创建的提示。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-t1cjenm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-t1cjenm","updated":"20250921104208"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-6s2ulxu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-6s2ulxu","updated":"20250921104208"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"C3："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"硬-软提示混合调优"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"(Hard-Soft Prompt Hybrid Tuning)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。与其使用一个纯粹可学习的提示模板，一些方法将这些可调的嵌入插入到一个硬提示模板中。Liu等人提出了“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"P-tuning"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"”，其中一些提示词元是通过可训练变量学习的，这些变量被插入到嵌入中。为了与提示词元交互，他们使用了一个BiLSTM来表示提示嵌入。P-tuning还在模板中引入了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"任务相关的锚点词元"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"（例如，关系提取中的“capital”）以进一步改进。这些锚点词元在训练期间不被调整。Han等人提出了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"带规则的提示调优（PTR）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"，它使用手动制作的子模板，通过逻辑规则来组成一个完整的模板。为了增强所得模板的表示能力，他们还插入了几个虚拟词元，其嵌入可以与预训练的LM参数一起使用训练样本进行调整。PTR中的模板词元包含实际词元和虚拟词元。实验结果证明了这种提示设计方法在关系分类任务中的有效性。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-magdrk5","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-magdrk5","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919170744-icxi3x9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-icxi3x9","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-hsi1q2y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-hsi1q2y","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一部分深入探讨了自动化模板学习的两种核心技术路线："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示（硬提示）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"和"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示（软提示）"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-owyx1jl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-owyx1jl","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示（硬提示）：在词语世界里寻宝"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-uupssn5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-uupssn5","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一派方法的目标是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"找到人类可读的最佳文字组合"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。它们都工作在离散的、符号化的空间里。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-8sotywc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-8sotywc","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-v4131k9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-v4131k9","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-9dyz5io","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-9dyz5io","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D1 - 挖掘 (Mining)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"：像个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"考古学家"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。在海量文本（如维基百科）中，找到能天然连接输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong code","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"和输出"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong code","TextMarkTextContent":"y"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"的那些“中间短语”。简单粗暴但有效。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-ax48p61","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ax48p61","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-66bqv7d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-66bqv7d","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D2 - 改写 (Paraphrasing)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"：像个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言大师"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。从一个还不错的“种子”提示出发，通过同义词替换、翻译往返等方式，创造出一大堆“变体”，然后优中选优。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-f6k4c7y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-f6k4c7y","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-tfn1vdy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-tfn1vdy","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D3 - 梯度搜索 (Gradient-based Search)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"：像个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"黑客"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。它不关心语法和语义，直接通过数学优化（梯度）的方法，一个词一个词地替换模板中的词元，直到找到能让模型输出正确答案的“咒语”（触发词）。这有点像对抗性攻击。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-r0gvual","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-r0gvual","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-1ialb6a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-1ialb6a","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D4 - 生成 (Generation)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"：像个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"作家"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。直接让另一个强大的生成模型（如T5）来“写”一个好提示。这是一种“模型教模型”的元学习思路。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-twm0919","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-twm0919","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919170744-ocg8w0l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-ocg8w0l","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"D5 - 评分 (Scoring)"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"：像个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"评委"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"。先准备一堆候选模板，然后让语言模型自己来判断，哪个模板填上答案后“读起来最通顺”（概率最高），就用哪个。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-1w6h0f6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-1w6h0f6","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示（软提示）：在向量空间里作画"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-i0qtyfe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-i0qtyfe","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这一派方法完全"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong strong","TextMarkTextContent":"摆脱了自然语言的束缚"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"，直接在模型能理解的数学空间（嵌入空间）里寻找最优的“提示向量”。这些提示对人类来说是无意义的乱码，但对模型来说却是最高效的指令。"}]},{"ID":"20250919170744-9drorq1","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919170744-9drorq1","updated":"20250919170744"},"Children":[{"ID":