erties":{"id":"20250919172337-eqvwt91","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-cq0p0v4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-cq0p0v4","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-gxycjob","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-gxycjob","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于输入“中国”，为了找出其首都，使用了三个不同的提示："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Subject: China; Relation: isCapital [MASK]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"China's capital is [MASK]."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"The capital of China is [MASK]."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-pe5pxeg","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-pe5pxeg","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-iz4p1z0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-iz4p1z0","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“兼听则明”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。用多种不同的方式问同一个问题，然后综合所有提问方式得到的答案，以期获得更稳定、更准确的结果。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-2z8fi1r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-2z8fi1r","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-6rxjlvz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-6rxjlvz","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"(b) 提示增强 (Prompt Augmentation)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-sx5haig","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-sx5haig","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-fy87n05","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-fy87n05","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-amg5ijr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-amg5ijr","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于输入“6, 8”，为了计算它们的和，在实际问题 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Input: Add up two numbers: 6, 8"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 之前，先给出了两个例子："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Ans-PR1: 1+1=2"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Ans-PR2: 2+5=7"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-75kmjwo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-75kmjwo","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-r32dgq9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-r32dgq9","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“举一反三”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。在提出真正的问题之前，先给模型看几个已经解决的类似问题的例子（即 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"(问题, 答案)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 对），让模型通过“上下文学习”（in-context learning）来理解任务的模式和要求。这就是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"少样本学习 (Few-shot Learning)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的典型范式。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-ga62p4g","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ga62p4g","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-wj4qewd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-wj4qewd","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"(c) 提示组合 (Prompt Composition)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-684t6iv","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-684t6iv","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-i3b982w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-i3b982w","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-7jaoo0m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-7jaoo0m","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于输入“谷歌成为Alphabet的子公司”，为了识别这个关系，将问题分解成几个子提示（"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Sub-PR1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Sub-PR3"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​），分别提取主语、宾语等，最后将这些子提示"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"组合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成一个完整的提示 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[X] The [MASK] Google [MASK] the [MASK] Alphabet."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 来让模型填充。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-5i5b7im","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-5i5b7im","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-afdq4so","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-afdq4so","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“分而治之，合而攻之”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。对于一个可以分解成多个子任务的复杂问题（如关系提取），先为每个子任务设计一个子提示，然后将这些子提示"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"拼接或组合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成一个更复杂的“超级提示”，一次性解决整个问题。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-uk0wub9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-uk0wub9","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-mxpt57u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-mxpt57u","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"(d) 提示分解 (Prompt Decomposition)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-krhe8rs","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-krhe8rs","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-ufu61bk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ufu61bk","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-t0j20qc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-t0j20qc","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：对于输入“迈克昨天去了纽约”，为了识别所有命名实体，将原始句子"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成多个跨度（如“迈克”、“纽约”），然后"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为每个跨度分别"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用一个提示（如 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"[X] Mike is [MASK] entity type."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​）来判断其实体类型。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-tvp4qkw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-tvp4qkw","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-ltmprq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ltmprq5","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"“化整为零，逐个击破”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。当一个输入需要做出多个预测时（如命名实体识别要标记出所有实体），直接用一个提示处理整个输入可能很困难。因此，将复杂的输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成多个更小的单元，然后"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"对每个单元独立使用一个简单的提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进行预测。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-iw1jw4y","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-iw1jw4y","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-d23c4km","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-d23c4km","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这张图直观地展示了超越“单一提问”的四种高级提示策略，它们的核心思想都是通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"组合和利用多个提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来增强模型的能力、稳定性和对复杂任务的处理能力。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-jybqkb9","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-jybqkb9","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-8mbm8d6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-8mbm8d6","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-a7y3xv6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-a7y3xv6","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"集成 vs. 增强"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示集成"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"并行"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的，用多个独立的提示问同一个问题，最后汇总结果。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示增强"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"串行"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的，用多个已回答的提示作为“上下文”或“示例”，来引导模型解决当前的问题。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-83wf8rw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-83wf8rw","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-986skev","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-986skev","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"组合 vs. 分解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这两个策略都处理复杂任务，但方向相反。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示组合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是将多个子提示"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"合并"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成一个大提示，试图"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"一次性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解决问题。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示分解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是将一个大问题"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"拆分"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"成多个小问题，用多个简单提示"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分步"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解决。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-v2k738w","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-v2k738w","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-rb6n5r3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-rb6n5r3","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心目的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：这些方法共同的目标是：(1) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"降低对单个“完美提示”的依赖"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（集成）；(2) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"更好地向模型传达任务意图"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（增强）；(3) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"处理超出单个简单提示能力的复杂任务"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（组合与分解）。这标志着提示工程从“寻找最佳单点”向“构建鲁棒系统”的演进。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-co1li3j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-co1li3j","updated":"20250919172653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5.1 提示集成 (Prompt Ensembling)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-5vtdwz5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-5vtdwz5","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示集成"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是为一个输入同时制作多个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"未回答的提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（unanswered prompts）的过程。图2(a)中展示了一个例子。多个提示可以是"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"或"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"连续提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这种提示集成的动机可以有(1)利用不同提示的互补优势，(2)缓解选择单个最佳提示具有挑战性的提示工程成本，以及(3)稳定下游任务的性能。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-xmufu5c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-xmufu5c","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提示集成与机器学习中历史悠久的集成方法相关，这些方法旨在将多个系统结合在一起。当前的研究借鉴了这些想法，以有效的方式组合来自不同提示的预测，如下所述。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-abfalcc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-abfalcc","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-for5cnq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-for5cnq","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-ggl5kcj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ggl5kcj","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"均匀平均 (Uniform averaging)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。使用多个提示时，组合预测最直观的方法是对来自不同提示的概率进行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"平均"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。具体来说，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"P(z|x) = (1/k) * Σ P(z|f_prompt,i(x))"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，其中"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"f_prompt,i(x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​是第i个提示。Jiang等人首先通过在训练集上选择具有最高准确率的提示来过滤提示，然后取从顶部K个提示中获得的平均对数概率，以计算单个词元在事实探测任务中[Z]位置的概率。Schick和Schütze在使用集成模型对未标记数据集进行标注时，也尝试了一种简单平均的方法。在执行文本生成评估时，Yuan等人将其表述为一个文本生成问题，并取使用不同提示获得的最终生成分数的平均值。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-bi41p48","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-bi41p48","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-57mktus","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-57mktus","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"加权平均 (Weighted averaging)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。对来自多个提示的结果进行简单平均很容易实现，但也可能不是最优的，因为一些提示可能比其他提示表现更好。为了解决这个问题，一些工作使用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"加权平均"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，其中每个提示都与一个权重相关联。权重通常是预先指定的，或使用训练集进行优化。Jiang等人通过最大化训练数据的目标输出概率来学习每个提示的权重。Qin和Eisner使用软提示参数提出了几乎相同的方法。此外，Qin和Eisner还引入了一种数据依赖的加权策略，其中提示的权重根据其在提示中出现的概率进行不同加权。Schick和Schütze以及Schick和Schütze在训练前根据每个提示在训练集上的准确率按比例设置权重。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-quxj3x3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-quxj3x3","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-4n88pki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-4n88pki","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多数投票 (Majority voting)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。对于分类任务，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多数投票"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"也可用于组合来自不同提示的结果。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-vdkp703","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-vdkp703","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-dyqe971","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-dyqe971","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"知识蒸馏 (Knowledge distillation)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。一个由深度学习模型组成的集成通常可以通过"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"知识蒸馏"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"被提炼成一个单一的模型，从而提高性能。为了融合这个想法，Schick和Schütze以及Schick和Schütze为每个手动创建的模板-答案对训练一个单独的模型，然后使用这个模型集成来标注一个未标记的数据集。然后，最终模型被训练以将知识从标注的数据集中蒸馏出来。Gao等人使用类似的方法来蒸馏他们自动生成的模板的集成。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-9b9hky4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-9b9hky4","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-ephh94w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ephh94w","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用于文本生成的提示集成 (Prompt ensembling for text generation)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。关于文本生成任务的提示集成工作相对较少（即，答案是一串词元而不是单个词元的任务）。一种简单的集成方法是使用标准方法，即根据序列中下一个词的概率生成输出序列"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"P(z_i|x, z_\u0026lt;i) = (1/k) * Σ P(z_i|f_prompt,i(x), z_\u0026lt;i)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。然而，Schick和Schütze训练一个单独的模型"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"P(z|f_prompt,i(x), x)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​，并存储每个精细调整的LM在内存中是不可行的。相反，他们首先通过平均所有模型的生成概率来解码生成。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-g0xrxox","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-g0xrxox","updated":"20250919172653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5.2 提示增强 (Prompt Augmentation)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-b1y32xl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-b1y32xl","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示增强"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，有时也称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"演示学习"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（demonstration learning），提供了几个额外的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"已回答的提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（answered prompts），可以用来演示LM应该如何为输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提供答案。例如，与其仅仅提供一个“中国的首都是[Z]”的提示，不如在它前面加上几个例子，比如“英国的首都是伦敦。日本的首都是东京。中国的首都是[Z]。”图2(b)中可以找到另一个加法任务的例子。这些少样本演示利用了强语言模型遵循重复模式的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-93050ga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-93050ga","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"虽然提示增强的想法很简单，但在使其有效方面有几个具有挑战性的方面，例如：(1) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"样本选择"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：我们如何选择最有效的例子？ (2) "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"样本排序"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：我们如何正确地排序所选的例子？"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-mczt111","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-mczt111","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-swfjmzd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-swfjmzd","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-k780u5e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-k780u5e","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"样本选择 (Sample Selection)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。研究人员发现，在少样本场景中使用的例子选择会导致结果从接近最先进水平到接近随机猜测的巨大差异。为了解决这个问题，Gao等人和Liu等人利用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"句子嵌入"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来采样与输入在嵌入空间中接近的例子。为了衡量在没有新任务训练的情况下执行新任务的泛化能力，Mishra等人提供了同时包含"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"正面和负面样本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的指令，并强调了应避免的事项。"}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-gy32dyf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-gy32dyf","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-m6pazri","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-m6pazri","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"样本排序 (Sample Ordering)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。Lu等人发现，提供的已回答提示的顺序在模型性能中扮演着重要角色，并提出了基于熵的方法来对不同的候选排列进行评分。Kumar和Talukdar为增强提示搜索一个好的训练样本排列，并在提示之间学习一个分隔符词元以获得进一步的性能提升。Yoo等人建议，与其安排多个已回答的提示到有序列表中，不如基于这些已回答的提示使用提示方法生成一个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"元提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（meta-prompt）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-4j6iba7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-4j6iba7","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提示增强与"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基于检索的方法"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"密切相关，这些方法提供更多的文本上下文以提高性能，这种方法在基于提示的学习中也显示出有效性。然而，关键区别在于，提示增强利用了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"问题和答案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，而更大的上下文学习则不然。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-3mcouge","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-3mcouge","updated":"20250919172653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5.3 提示组合 (Prompt Composition)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-ua0bt01","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ua0bt01","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于那些可以基于多个更基础的子任务进行组合的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"可组合任务"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，我们也可以使用多个子提示执行"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示组合"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，每个子任务一个，然后基于这些子提示定义一个组合提示。这个过程在图2(c)中进行了说明。例如，在关系提取任务中，该任务旨在提取两个实体之间的关系，我们可以将该任务分解为多个子任务，包括识别实体的特征并对它们之间的关系进行分类。基于这种直觉，Han等人首先使用多个手动创建的子提示进行实体识别和关系分类，然后使用逻辑规则将它们组合成一个完整的关系提取提示。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-hg9qfdd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-hg9qfdd","updated":"20250919172653"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5.4 提示分解 (Prompt Decomposition)"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-mb9tkdv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-mb9tkdv","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于一个输入样本需要执行多个预测的任务（例如，序列标注），直接使用一个处理整个输入文本"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"x"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的整体提示是具有挑战性的。一个直观的解决方法是将整体提示分解为多个"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"子提示"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，并分别回答每个子提示。图2(d)用一个命名实体识别任务的例子说明了这个想法，该任务旨在识别输入句子中的所有命名实体。在这种情况下，输入将首先被转换成一组文本跨度，然后模型可以被提示预测实体类型（包括“非实体”）为每个跨度。由于跨度的数量很大，同时预测所有跨度类型是不容易的。因此，为每个跨度创建和预测不同的提示是可取的。Cui等人对命名实体识别使用了这种"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示分解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的方法，他们在这里应用了我们讨论过的方法。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-s2wq3yl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"1","id":"20250919172337-s2wq3yl","updated":"20250919172338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20250919172337-6y9lpf9","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-6y9lpf9","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"综合性解析"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-9uiaiww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-9uiaiww","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第五章将视野从“如何设计单个最佳提示”提升到了一个更宏观、更系统的层面——“"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如何协同使用多个提示来解决更复杂、更鲁棒的问题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”。这标志着提示工程从“点”的优化进入了“面”的构建。本章介绍的四种核心方法——集成、增强、组合和分解——为利用多个提示提供了四种截然不同的哲学和策略。"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-s3s8rad","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-s3s8rad","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-ha0l4r2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-ha0l4r2","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-98ekesp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-98ekesp","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示集成 (Prompt Ensembling)：追求稳定与鲁棒的“集体智慧”"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-3yubpby","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-3yubpby","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-4yqusqa","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-4yqusqa","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-247et4z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-247et4z","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心哲学"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：“不要把所有鸡蛋放在一个篮子里。” 任何单个提示都可能有其固有的偏见或弱点。通过用多种方式提问（比如用不同的措辞问“中国的首都是哪里？”），然后综合所有答案（通过平均、投票等方式），可以有效"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"平滑掉单个提示的极端表现，获得一个更稳定、更可靠的平均结果"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这是一种典型的用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"冗余换取鲁棒性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的策略，极大地降低了找到那个唯一“完美提示”的压力。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-3l16ie0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-3l16ie0","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-lhnfzyx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-lhnfzyx","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示增强 (Prompt Augmentation)：模仿与学习的“情境教学”"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-07ntz1y","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-07ntz1y","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-vrsgw3k","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-vrsgw3k","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-4d4182i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-4d4182i","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心哲学"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：“授人以鱼不如授人以渔。” 与其直接问一个零样本问题，不如先给模型看几个“例题”和“标准答案”。这利用了大语言模型强大的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模式识别"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"上下文学习 (In-context Learning)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 能力。模型通过观察示例，能够"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"动态地、在不更新参数的情况下“领悟”到当前任务的规则和意图"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这就是少样本学习（Few-shot Learning）的精髓。然而，其效果对"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"例子的选择和排序"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"极为敏感，这也催生了如何智能挑选“好老师”（即好例子）的研究。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-qn3qnje","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-qn3qnje","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-f9e2lsx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-f9e2lsx","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示组合 (Prompt Composition)：化零为整的“模块化构建”"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-udb3rae","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-udb3rae","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-5x61fbx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-5x61fbx","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-gojzu3j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-gojzu3j","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心哲学"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：“聚沙成塔。” 对于一个可以自然分解为多个步骤的复杂任务（如关系提取 = 识别实体A + 识别实体B + 判断A与B的关系），我们可以为每个步骤设计一个简单的“子提示”，然后"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"像搭积木一样将这些子提示拼接成一个复杂的“超级提示”"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这种方法使得处理多阶段、结构化的任务成为可能，体现了"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模块化设计"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的思想。"}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-0yl5syb","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-0yl5syb","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-3mbvpwn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-3mbvpwn","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提示分解 (Prompt Decomposition)：化整为零的“分治策略”"}]},{"ID":"20250919172337-sncjmr3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-sncjmr3","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-us403qq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-us403qq","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250919172337-frq1rvk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250919172337-frq1rvk","updated":"20250919172337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心哲学"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：“庖丁解牛。” 当一个任务需要在"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同一个输入上做出多个独立的预测"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时（如命名实体识别需要标记出句子中所有的实体），试图用一个大而全的提示一次性完成所有工作会非常困难。更明智的做法是，先将复杂的输入"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"拆解成多个独立的、更小的处理单元"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（如将句子拆成词或短语），然后"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为每个单元重复使用一个简单的提示进行预测"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这是一种经典的“分而治之”策略，用多次简单的调用来代替一次复杂的调用。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":